abstrac: I offer medical billing services and have over 14 years of extensive experience using many different types of billing software.
bio:
I have been medical billing for greater than 14 years. I have submitted claims for Blue Cross/Blue Shield, Medicare, Medicaid, No fault eligibility, Commercial, Automotive, Workman's Comp., Third Party, and home health care billing. I have worked for various hospitals, Oncology physicians, Hand Surgery specialists, Orthopedic surgeons, general practice doctors, Chiropractic doctors and massage therapists.

Furthermore, I have experience using many different types of software including: Misys, E-Thomas, Medical Manager, MBS, Medic, Healthmatic Nterprise, Alora Home Healthcare software and various Microsoft Office programs.
I generally work business hours due to the hours that many insurance companies are open.  Depending on the job or the type of work, I can work after hours or even weekends.
